"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1佢都鍾意我<br />\n2才華<br />\n3唔自私<br />\n4有taste <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他唔係好睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2.有錢咪有才華囉<br />\n3.有錢咪唔洗自私囉<br />\n4.有錢咪有得講taste囉<br />\n1.集齊以上條件再鐘意你先有得幫你埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652954eeb5a3963e1de0ebe9177b606aa506666d","tid":504481,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>揀乜撚都假，一定要有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上進心</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一定要有才華</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEg?</blockquote><br />\nEg條撚咩，啲臭閪一個上進心同才華無限演繹，講撚晒啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf39058f315a20bcfa8eaad9669e2464ceb667b4","tid":504481,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"樣先<br />\n無樣真係幾好心地都無用<br />\n性格<br />\n腿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa026320d7ca22fa1de8ed9c11dafbbc2d8675cf","tid":504481,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"如果係好悶既人呢?"},{"pid":"85fe073bfd0b6819932baf36e2d0be509b8e77b7","tid":504481,"uid":55391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>揀乜撚都假，一定要有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上進心</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一定要有才華</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEg?</blockquote><br />\nEg條撚咩，啲臭閪一個上進心同才華無限演繹，講撚晒啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n變錢出嚟既才華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f1929c166a6fe5556fa54d8d856a5aeca044b2","tid":504481,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"其實講咁多<